                            <comment id="17246123" author="chrylis" created="Tue, 8 Dec 2020 20:05:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My apologies; I was trying to get out the door and forgot to mention that yes, this only applies in the context of &lt;tt&gt;@CompileStatic&lt;/tt&gt; (otherwise, the compiler would select a MethodClosure instead, which is the workaround I&apos;m using). I haven&apos;t had the chance to MCVE it yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
